headline: Regions Bank Included Among HUD’s Fiscal Year 2024 Top Lenders
summary: BIRMINGHAM, Ala., February 26, 2025--Regions Bank on Wednesday announced its Real Estate Capital Markets division, a national multifamily and health care real estate lender, achieved a top lender ranking in four categories from the U.S. Department of Housing and Urban Development (HUD).
